      <section class="brand--department-of-energy-climate-change brand__border-color organisation__brand-border-top organisation__margin-bottom" id="freedom-of-information">
    <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding  ">Make an FOI request</h2>


    
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak ">
    
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>
            Read about the Freedom of Information (FOI) Act and <a href="https://www.gov.uk/make-a-freedom-of-information-request/the-freedom-of-information-act" class="brand__color">how to make a request</a>.
          </li>
          <li>
            Check <a href="/government/publications?departments%5B%5D=department-for-exiting-the-european-union&amp;publication_type=foi-releases" class="brand__color">our previous releases</a> to see if we’ve already answered your question.
          </li>
            <li>Make a new request by contacting us using the details below.</li>
        </ol>

</div>

        <div class="organisation__contact-section ">
